The Glenn Beck Show PODCAST OCT-03-2013 THURS







The Glenn Beck Program

          
Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET
        

      

      
The Glenn Beck Program - 10/3/13





Thursday, October 03, 2013 10:29 AM



Glenn Beck sheds light on the truth about the president inflicting pain to push through 
 the government shutdown and pass Obamacare,
 even thought sign ups for it are very low. 

 Also, Ted Cruz joins the show and let's everyone know "we are winning this fight." 

  Plus, Glenn warns hyperinflation is around the corner and asks the American people to #DefundtheGOP.
